design skills  \\n     – Good communication & structured problem solving  \\n   • Identified gaps:\\n     – Limited Terraform experience (basic)  \\n     – No prior Kubernetes production deployments (entry-level)  \\n   • Recommendation:\\n     – Strong fit for Senior Backend Engineer role with minor onboarding on Kubernetes  \\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"# **The Overall Goal**\\n\\nYour task is to take interview. The following are the steps\\n-\\\"Analyze the job description\\\",\\n    \\\"Analyze the candidate resume\\\",\\n    \\\"Conduct technical interview\\\",\\n    \\\"Send emails as and when needed\\\",\\n    \\\"Score candidate responses\\\",\\n    \\\"Generate final evaluation report\\\"\\n\\nReturn the output as a .txt file of all the steps taken to perform the tasks.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n---\\n# **Context from Upstream Tasks**\\nNo completed previous tasks context available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task2:\\n  Objective: Send scheduling and follow-up emails to the candidate and interview panel based on analysis outputs.\\nTask task3:\\n  Objective: Conduct the technical interview using prepared questions aligned to the job description and resume insights.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nAnalyze the candidate’s resume to identify relevant experience and technical strengths.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPlain text\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```txt\\nInterview Process Summary\\n\\n1. Analyze Job Description\\n   • Reviewed the posted role: “Senior Backend Engineer”  \\n   • Extracted core requirements:\\n     – Strong Java & Spring Boot experience  \\n     – Microservices architecture & REST API design  \\n     – AWS (EC2, S3, RDS) deployment  \\n     – Docker/Kubernetes containerization  \\n     – Agile/Scrum development process  \\n\\n2. Analyze Candidate Resume\\n   • Relevant Experience:\\n     – Software Engineer at Acme Corp (Jan 2019 – Present)\\n  