\\nTime: 10:00 AM – 11:00 AM PST  \\nLocation: Zoom Meeting ([Meeting Link])  \\nInterviewers: John Doe (Data Engineering Lead), Jane Smith (Cloud Architect)\\n\\nPlease come prepared to discuss:\\n- Your microservices and AWS migration projects  \\n- Designing optimized data pipelines and Spark job tuning  \\n- Data warehousing and ETL best practices  \\n\\nKindly confirm your availability by Monday, April 29. We look forward to speaking with you.\\n\\nBest regards,  \\n[Your Name]  \\n[Your Title]  \\n[Company]  \\n[Your Email] | [Your Phone]\\n\\n------------------------------\\nEMAIL 2:\\nTo: John Doe <john.doe@[company].com>, Jane Smith <jane.smith@[company].com>\\nSubject: Confirmation: Technical Interview with [Candidate Name]\\n\\nHello John and Jane,\\n\\nThis is a confirmation for the technical interview with [Candidate Name] for the Senior Data Engineer position.\\n\\nDate: Wednesday, May 3, 2024  \\nTime: 10:00 AM – 11:00 AM PST  \\nLocation: Zoom Meeting ([Meeting Link])\\n\\nPlease review the candidate's resume and the job description prior to the interview, focusing on their experience with microservices, AWS migration, and data pipeline design.\\n\\nThank you for your time.\\n\\nRegards,  \\n[Your Name]  \\n[Your Title]  \\n[Company]  \\n[Your Email] | [Your Phone]\\n\\n------------------------------\\nEMAIL 3:\\nTo: [Candidate Name] <[candidate.email@example.com]>\\nSubject: Thank You for Interviewing with [Company]\\n\\nDear [Candidate Name],\\n\\nThank you for taking the time to meet with us today. We enjoyed learning about:\\n- Your approach to designing scalable microservices  \\n- Strategies you’ve used to optimize Spark jobs  \\n- Your experience building and migrating data pipelines on AWS  \\n\\nWe will review our notes and get back to you with next steps by Friday, May 10. If you have any follow-up questions, feel free to reply to this email.\\n\\nBest regards,  \\n[Your Name]  \\n[Your Title]  \\n[Company]  \\n[Your Email] | [Your Phone]\\n\\n------------------------------\\nEMAIL 4:\\nTo: John Doe <john.doe@[company].com>, Jane Smith <jane.smith@[company].com>\\nSubject: Request for Interview Feedback: [Candidate Name]\\n\\nHello John and Jane,\\n\\nThank you for conducting the technical interview with [Candidate Name] today. Please provide your feedback on the candidate’s:\\n- Technical skills (Java, AWS, Spark)  \\n- Problem-solving approach  \\n- Communication and collaboration  \\n\\nReply to this email with your comments by Wednesday, May 8, so we can finalize our evaluation.\\n\\nThanks in advance for your prompt response.\\n\\nRegards,  \\n[Your Name]  \\n[Your Title]  \\n[Company]  \\n[Your Email] | [Your Phone]\\n\"}"}
