all Total: 69 / 75\\n\\n6. Generate Final Evaluation Report\\n   - Strengths: Strong knowledge of data pipeline design. Excellent communication skills.\\n   - Weaknesses: Limited experience with specific cloud technologies like Azure Databricks.\\n   - Recommendation: Hire\\n```\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nNo downstream objectives available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nGenerate the final evaluation report summarizing scores, strengths, weaknesses, and recommendations.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPlain text (.txt)\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```text\\nFinal Evaluation Report:\\n\\nCandidate: [Candidate Name]\\n\\nScoring Breakdown:\\n  - Technical Accuracy: 23 / 25\\n  - Problem-Solving Approach: 23 / 25\\n  - Communication & Clarity: 23 / 25\\n  - Overall Total: 69 / 75\\n\\nSummary:\\nThe candidate demonstrated strong knowledge of data pipeline design and optimization techniques. They also exhibited excellent communication skills and clarity in explaining complex concepts.\\n\\nStrengths:\\n  - Strong understanding of data pipeline design principles.\\n  - Excellent problem-solving abilities in data-related scenarios.\\n  - Clear and effective communication skills.\\n\\nWeaknesses:\\n  - Limited practical experience with specific cloud technologies such as Azure Databricks, as the resume highlights more experience with AWS.\\n\\nRecommendations:\\nHire\\n```\\n\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-28T12:23:43.353386\"\n}"}
